Package: nexus-open
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libusb-1.0-0 (>= 2:1.0.21), libayatana-appindicator3-1
Recommends: flutter
Maintainer: Matt <matthew.panton@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/mantonx/nexus-next
Description: Linux controller for Corsair iCUE Nexus display
 Nexus Open provides a native Linux desktop application to control
 and configure your Corsair iCUE Nexus (640x48 pixel display).
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time system monitoring (CPU/GPU temperatures, network stats)
  - Weather display with location-based updates
  - Custom backgrounds and color schemes
  - Touch input support
  - REST API for programmatic control
  - Flutter-based configuration UI
